rows.label: qst103108_msg0001
rows.name:
Hmm. You certainly look pleased
with yourselves. What happened?

rows.label: qst103108_msg0002
rows.name: Hmm hmm. What's this? A key?

rows.label: qst103108_msg0003
rows.name:
Judging by the carvings, I'd say
this is an ancient Nopon artifact
just like the murals. What a find!

rows.label: qst103108_msg0004
rows.name: But it seems we are lacking a keyhole.

rows.label: qst103108_msg0005
rows.name:
You take this. You have a
better chance of finding
the keyhole than I do.

rows.label: qst103108_msg0006
rows.name: I pray you find a keyhole to fit it.

rows.label: qst103108_msg0007
rows.name:
As for me...it would be a shame
to simply return to Superbia.

rows.label: qst103108_msg0008
rows.name:
I think I shall stay here and study
the murals in greater depth.

rows.label: qst103108_msg0009
rows.name:
You've been an immense help.
Thank you for everything.
